title: Anvil - Speed of Sound (Japanese Version) [FLAC]
description:
This is the super rare Japanese pressing of Anvil's 1999 album "Speed of Sound", complete with two highly sought after extra studio tracks not found anywhere else.

For maximum enjoyment, this album has been ripped in EAC and encoded in FLAC and for proof of authenticity, I scanned all of the album's artwork.

Fans of Anvil and classic Heavy Metal will definitely enjoy this very rare release in lossless form
